snippet.textDisplay: This is why I LOVE that bitch! Her talent is flawless and she does it with the exact flair and without pulling those constipation expressions, and letting her double chin relax. And at last, the old Mariah Carey is back and her body isn’t struggling and suffocating in clothes 6 sizes too small. Embrace yourself, and give a finger to that obnoxious diva faking attitude that belongs in the Bronx ghetto from the 1980s, (I blame that Jerry Springer show for that!) The Mariah Carey from back when, she had that flawless voice and her talent was her beauty, not this arrogant rude creature she became, and if that what money turns you into, nah leave me poor! After seeing this incredible video, if anything we’ve learnt from this brutal Coronavirus Pandemic, I hope it would be no matter your talent and/or wealthy, humanity and humility is free and it helps to heal the world we all belong and live upon, so give up your rudeness and thinking you’re better than everyone else, I mean Coronavirus doesn’t care who you are, so just be kind and care. Mariah Carey, bravo to this incredible clip and I still have your songs in my heart from the beginning, so chill and please simply be YOU, from the beginning of your career
